Package br.com.framework.annotation

Interface Summary
AnnotationReader<T> Defines the methods for all the annotations readers.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAnnotationReader<T> This class is responsible for reading the annotations of an object.
ClassAnnotationReader<T>  
 

Annotation Types Summary
Parallel This annotation defines which method in the class should be executed in parallel.
Thread This annotation defines a class as a thread.
ThreadConstructor This annotation should be used to mark the constructor that must be called if for some reason the framework has to create a new object for this thread.
